{"title":"浪花小集","authors":["董茂棠"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":11,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花小集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董茂棠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海螺死时留下了遗产——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一间螺旋形的小屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没盛珍珠但不贫穷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声在里面凝固成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力的结晶体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做成号——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能吹出征服大海的音响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆是针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握在渔家粗糙但不笨拙的手指。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着海平线飞针走线——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把天和海缝合成一个巨型的网。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙宫的珠玉和金银首饰一网网捞回港湾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舢板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大海把你戏弄？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛下波谷又举上浪峰……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻飞的鸥鸟用浪打湿的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻阅着海的常识——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，大海把年青的摇橹手收为弟子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在正举行特殊的欢迎仪式……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}